sequenceDiagram
  autonumber

  participant U as Shopper
  participant W as Web (Next.js)
  participant A as Core API (NestJS)
  participant S as Stripe
  participant DB as PostgreSQL
  participant R as Redis Queue
  participant WK as Worker (NestJS)
  participant E as Resend

  U->>W: Start checkout
  W->>A: POST /checkout/session
  A->>DB: Validate cart + create/reuse checkout session
  A-->>W: sessionToken + pricing + readiness

  U->>W: Submit address/contact + Pay now
  W->>A: POST /checkout/session/:token/payment
  A->>S: Create hosted checkout session
  S-->>A: providerSessionId + checkoutUrl
  A-->>W: checkoutUrl
  W->>S: Redirect to hosted checkout

  S-->>A: POST /webhooks/stripe (checkout.session.*)
  A->>DB: Upsert webhook event + claim processing lock
  A->>DB: Reconcile by providerSessionId
  alt Payment paid
    A->>DB: Transaction: create order, line items, decrement stock, clear cart
    A->>R: Enqueue SEND_ORDER_CONFIRMATION job
  else Not paid / terminal failure
    A->>DB: Mark waiting/canceled/failed state
  end

  par Return-flow finalization
    W->>A: GET /checkout/session/:token/payment-status
    A->>S: Retrieve checkout session status
    A-->>W: paid/open/canceled/expired
    W->>A: POST /checkout/place-order (idempotencyKey)
    A-->>W: orderNumber
  and Async email delivery
    WK->>R: Consume SEND_ORDER_CONFIRMATION job
    WK->>DB: Read order snapshot
    WK->>E: Send order confirmation email
  end

  W-->>U: Redirect to /orders/:orderNumber
